{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dd05e25bef","title":"给郭沫若“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d718da885b","index":0,"year":1944,"month":1,"day":9,"articleId":"dd05e25bef"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7a71578b5e","type":"paragraph","text":"给郭沫若“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"dd05e25bef"},{"id":"8a16945254","type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年1月9日）郭沫若兄收到《虎符》，全篇读过，深为感动。你做了许多十分有益的革命的文化工作，我向你表示庆贺","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"dd05e25bef"},{"id":"b6904ac237","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"dd05e25bef"},{"id":"ef37c03dfa","type":"paragraph","text":"一月九日延安[1]郭沫若（1892-1978），四川乐山人，历史学案、文学家和革命活动家。抗田战争时期，曾在周思来任副部长的国民政府军事受员会政治部任第三厅厅长、文化工作委员会主任，在国民党统治区组织进步文化人士从事抗日宣传工作。[2]《虎符》，是郭沫若1942年2月写的一部历史话剧。副本取材于战国时期独国信陵君和安整王的宠境如姬罚符技赵的故事，借此宣传爱国主义思想，从西护击国民党的卖国投降政策和搭残花数力量的暴行","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"dd05e25bef"}],"page":{"id":"35978c3a28","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"dd05e25bef","start":301,"end":301}}}},"__N_SSG":true}